descript.abstract: Subdivision polygons in Dakota County for the purpose of labeling. CIC's will not be labeled as they are part of their original underlying subdivision plat.
descript.purpose: For general mapping use to depict property subdivisions.

procstep.procdesc: Parcel polygons are merged based on the portion of their PIN that relates to the Plat they are part of. The plat names and book and page numbers are then added by join from Plat Tracking database.
